{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1879","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","text":"MLNAnnotationView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"identifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"identifier","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A string identifying the annotation view to be reused."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This string is the same one you specify when initially returning the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation view object using the "},{"code":"-mapView:viewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An annotation view object with the given identifier, or "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if no"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such object exists in the reuse queue."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For performance reasons, you should generally reuse ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects for identical-looking annotations in your map views. Dequeueing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"saves time and memory during performance-critical operations such as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"scrolling.","type":"text"}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}]}}}